assertions.assertion:
The function
int pthread_attr_getschedparam(const pthread_attr_t *restrict attr, contst struct sched_param *restrict param);
gets the scheduling parameter attributes in the 'attr' argument. The contents of the 'param' structure are defined in sched.h. For the SCHED_FIFO and SCHED_RR policies, the only required member of 'param' is 'sched_priority'.
